<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/143003021/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """Evaluation is based in a projects consisting in the application of the different models to the analysis of the aerodynamics of a given spacecraft.
The project is done in groups of four and the presentation done by one of the group members.

A final exam is also possible for those that not follow the project evaluation."""@es ;
